      "input": " Interface          Grp  A-F Pri  Time Own Pre State   Master addr/Group addr\n  Vl10                 1 IPv4 150     0  N   Y  MASTER  10.1.0.1(local) 10.1.0.3\n  Vl11                 2 IPv4 150     0  N   Y  MASTER  10.1.1.1(local) 10.1.1.3\n  Vl12                 3 IPv4 100     0  Y   Y  BACKUP  10.1.2.5 10.1.2.3\n  Vl13                 4 IPv4 150     0  N   N  INIT    10.1.3.1(local) 10.1.3.3\n",
